Usage: from Damian Conway vedio!
```
vmap <expr> <LEFT> DVB_Drag('left')
vmap <expr> <RIGHT> DVB_Drag('right')
vmap <expr> <DOWN> DVB_Drag('down')
vmap <expr> <UP> DVB_Drag('up')
vmap <expr> D    DVB_Duplicate()
```
